  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AdultMaze
    Non-limited maze design with difficulties ranging from easy to advanced.
    Cell
    Each row and column of a maze consists of a single cell.
    ChildrenMaze
    An overall easier maze design for a younger audience with a few additions.
    Logo
    Logo that is an image that can be placed in the maze as a Wall
    Main
     
    Maze
    Stores essential maze data and communicates with other classes.

    Generates a maze to be displayed and edited.

    Cell type used in Children Mazes to indicate the start and end of a maze with images
